OL,3,CDozens arrested in Paris after
OL,4,Cviolence erupts after PSG's Champions
OL,5,CLeague win
OL,7,FDozens of people have been arrested in
OL,8,FFrance after violence broke out during
OL,9,Fcelebrations for Paris Saint-Germain's
OL,10,Fsecond Champions League title win.
OL,12,FAbout 20,000 people gathered on the
OL,13,FChamps-Elysees after PSG beat Arsenal
OL,14,Fon penalties in a dramatic final in
OL,15,FBudapest.
OL,17,FFans marched along the avenues near
OL,18,Fthe Arc de Triomphe, with some setting
OL,19,Foff flares and blaring car horns.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
