OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780275788
OL,3,CDozens arrested in Paris after
OL,4,Cviolence erupts after PSG's Champions
OL,5,CLeague win
OL,7,FA group tried to storm a police
OL,8,Fstation in the French capital while
OL,9,Facross the city, shops were vandalised
OL,10,Fand cars set on fire.
OL,12,FParis police said that by 10 p.m., 45
OL,13,Fpeople were taken into custody.
OL,15,FOfficers also contained about 1,000
OL,16,Fpeople gathered near the PSG stadium
OL,17,Fin the 16th Arrondissement and cleared
OL,18,Fbarricades made from bicycles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
