OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780275788
OL,3,CDozens arrested in Paris after
OL,4,Cviolence erupts after PSG's Champions
OL,5,CLeague win
OL,7,FIn May last year following PSG's first
OL,8,Ftitle, when 201 people were injured in
OL,9,Fthe French capital and police made
OL,10,Fmore than 500 arrests across France,
OL,11,FParis was on high alert, with 8,000
OL,12,Fpolice officers deployed across the
OL,13,Fcity.
OL,15,FPSG's victory deprived the Gunners of
OL,16,Fwhat could have been their first
OL,17,FChampions League title in their 140-
OL,18,Fyear history ` hot off the heels of
OL,19,Ftheir first Premier League title in 22
OL,20,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
