OL,3,CDozens arrested in Paris after
OL,4,Cviolence erupts after PSG's Champions
OL,5,CLeague win
OL,7,FSaturday's match at Budapest's Puskas
OL,8,FArena was 1-1 at the end of regulation
OL,9,Ftime and extra time, as Kai Havertz's
OL,10,Fsixth-minute opener was cancelled out
OL,11,Fby Ousmane Dembele's second-half
OL,12,Fpenalty.
OL,14,FArsenal defender Gabriel Magalhaes
OL,15,Ffired the last of his team's penalties
OL,16,Fover the bar, while Eberechi Eze also
OL,17,Fmissed his shot, handing PSG a 4-3
OL,18,Fshootout victory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
